<COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">Gen. Gromov himself</COREF> said Soviet troops expected to leave behind more than $ 1 billion of military equipment and installations for <COREF ID="28" TYPE="IDENT">the <COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT">Kabul</COREF> regime</COREF> .
