For months <COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT">the resistance</COREF> has been defenseless against air attack .
Thus far there is no indication that <COREF ID="19" TYPE="IDENT">they</COREF> have been re-supplied with Stingers or other anti-aircraft weapons .
